titleNullable: Human Protein Atlas - Yellow Cell Tile Dataset
subtitleNullable: Individual Cells From the HPA Competition Data - Yellow Channel Only (ER)
descriptionNullable:
### Context

Create a dataset to help with the HPA Protein Localization Competition


### Content

This dataset contains individual, square, images of cells from the larger images that had only one label. This will not guarantee that the cell-level label is accurate and may still require additional processing.

**I apologize in advance for the weird folder structure. It's due to zipping and was an unfortunate by-product**

### Acknowledgements

Thanks to the competition authors and user Tito for his mask dataset


### Inspiration

This is exactly how I would do it if I was tasked to do this task manually.
